---
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-10">
  <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold leading-[1.15] mb-6 md:whitespace-nowrap">
    Strategy, execution, and support
  </h1>
  <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[var(--color-slate)] max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
    A marketing agency with the experience to plan, the skills to deliver and the structure to support.
  </p>
  <a
    href="/contact"
    class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-paper)] border border-[var(--color-line)] px-8 py-5 text-lg text-[var(--color-ink)] hover:border-[var(--color-slate)] transition-colors"
  >
    <span
      class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full shrink-0 ring-2 ring-white"
      style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, #f2789a 0%, var(--color-accent) 60%, #c72f5e 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 14px 3px rgba(232, 70, 124, 0.5);"
    ></span>
    What brings you here?
  </a>
</div>
